    public static final class Metadata.BlockMetadata.Builder

implements Metadata.BlockMetadataOrBuilder
     BlockMetadata stores data used by the Raft OSNs when
 coordinating with each other, to be serialized into
 block meta dta field and used after failres and restarts.
    Protobuf type etcdraft.BlockMetadata
